WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:01:01.839
Subtitles and audio translation will begin later. Please wait for the official start of the video.

00:01:01.840 --> 00:01:07.023
Well, good evening, family. Thank you for joining us again today.

00:01:07.024 --> 00:01:17.282
We're going to go over some things some people have had questions concerning our ministry and why we're named what we're named and all things like that.

00:01:17.283 --> 00:01:21.599
So, we want to clear some things up because we've had some emails. Some are not so nice.

00:01:21.600 --> 00:01:28.354
People are pretty upset about things being, you know, sister clipboards or whatever you want to call them because they don't understand.

00:01:28.355 --> 00:01:38.289
But Diana wants to explain the foundation part of our name. We are not a foundation, for sure. I want you to know that we are not a foundation.

00:01:38.290 --> 00:01:53.954
We picked the name because prayer is a foundation, but we're an online church, and so the Prayer Changes Things Foundation is an online church if you see that in the description that we put in there.

00:01:53.955 --> 00:02:08.278
We have weekly online services, and so under US federal law, churches are automatically recognized as tax-exempt under section 501(c)(3) of the IRS and are not required to apply for formal recognition.

00:02:08.279 --> 00:02:19.079
So, we have an EIN and all of that, but we don't have to do what some of the more... like Joseph Z's ministry has a board and all.

00:02:19.080 --> 00:02:34.376
There are more requirements and stuff that they all do, but churches are also specifically exempt from the Form 990 filing requirement under the Internal Revenue Code 6033A 3 AI.

00:02:34.377 --> 00:02:43.574
So, everything we've done—I want to say this because people want to know because it's tax season—everything we have done, we have gone through lawyers.

00:02:43.575 --> 00:02:55.793
We have gone through people that have set it up that have been professional. My wife has a Master's degree in accounting.

00:02:55.794 --> 00:03:10.079
So, a lot of times you say, 'Well, Brandon, how come Diana is not on the broadcast today?'I want to tell you this—and we don't tell our business to everybody about everything—but she has a Master's degree in accounting and in business.

00:03:10.080 --> 00:03:13.483
She graduated top of her class. I was proud of her. I wanted to show her awards.

00:03:13.484 --> 00:03:22.152
She got her Summa Cum Laude awards. She got all her awards from ORU. She got her degree in accounting.

00:03:22.153 --> 00:03:28.039
She is very educated, and she graduated top of her class as she got awards and everything.

00:03:28.040 --> 00:03:33.680
So, I want you to know a lot of times it's not that she is trying to avoid prayer with everybody.

00:03:33.681 --> 00:03:44.998
Why is Diana not here? How come she doesn't want to be a part? She's working a full-time job. She's very educated. She's been working at this for years.

00:03:44.999 --> 00:03:54.945
And I didn't want her to give up her career of what she was doing, selling on eBay and Poshmark and doing the things that she has done for this.

00:03:54.946 --> 00:04:01.799
We don't depend on the ministry for finances. My wife works full-time.

00:04:01.800 --> 00:04:08.307
I do YouTube. We have a ministry property. The ministry has purchased a ministry property.

00:04:08.308 --> 00:04:11.479
That's different. I'm going to be straight up front with you.

00:04:11.480 --> 00:04:17.682
That is totally different. We did buy a ministry property. So, it's not shocking and all.

00:04:17.683 --> 00:04:22.988
When you have as much coming through, when you have this many people coming through, money flows through here.

00:04:22.989 --> 00:04:30.050
And I'm going to tell you this: I have never taken a vow of poverty. I'm not afraid of what I have. I'm not ashamed of what I have.

00:04:30.051 --> 00:04:43.079
I'm going to tell you this: I was instructed by the FBI to get a safe haven for me and my family because I've had threats on my life all the time on a consistent basis.

00:04:43.080 --> 00:04:49.654
Where we were at our old house, we have people showing up knocking on our door.

00:04:49.655 --> 00:05:01.824
And I'm going to tell you this: when you have an audience like we do and the people that hate us as much as they do, I just want to tell you, I have to protect my family.

00:05:01.825 --> 00:05:05.156
Now, we have attorneys. We've had to hire full-time security.

00:05:05.157 --> 00:05:22.823
We're having to look into full-time security to have to watch over me because of the incidents, but because of what I've been told by the sheriff's department, local law enforcement, and the FBI, I must provide protection for my family because of these threats, and they tell me they're legitimate.

00:05:22.824 --> 00:05:32.679
Now, I try to be as transparent as I can. I try not to tell where my address is and things like that because I have people that have tried to physically hurt me.

00:05:32.680 --> 00:05:41.014
So, if you think, 'Well, Brandon, you're secretive,'you don't understand Charlie Kirk was real. Do you understand that?

00:05:41.015 --> 00:05:48.959
So, when I feel a need and I feel it in my spirit to leave and go stay in a hotel that night, it's because the Lord's warning me to.

00:05:48.960 --> 00:06:03.051
I've had crazy people stay at IHOP for seven days demanding me to give them a word, and they thought they had a word, and they shaved their heads to look just like me and drive around the same place as I have.

00:06:03.052 --> 00:06:08.639
I have nuts follow us. And I'm just being quite frank; I don't ever talk about it.

00:06:08.640 --> 00:06:14.243
We don't talk about all this stuff, but there's a lot of emails and there's been a lot of hate lately about what I do with my life.

00:06:14.244 --> 00:06:22.538
And I don't tell you everything because I'm trying to keep my family safe, okay? There are a lot of people that hate me. Yes.

00:06:22.539 --> 00:06:34.079
And you have no idea what happens behind closed doors and the conversations that I have strictly with... Should I say that? No.

00:06:34.080 --> 00:06:40.679
Yeah, some of the people that I contact are in direct contact with the President of the United States of America.

00:06:40.680 --> 00:06:47.102
The messages that I deliver are received by the White House.

00:06:47.103 --> 00:06:54.949
I've told you I have been invited to the White House more than once, and I have turned it down every single time.

00:06:54.950 --> 00:07:00.964
I'm trying to tell you all, I don't try to come on here and be all haughty and say, 'Look at me.'It's not about Brandon.

00:07:00.965 --> 00:07:13.794
But people look at accuracy, and whenever they see things that you don't know that they know and they say, 'How did you find this out?'So they say, 'How did you know this?'I've been asked that many times.

00:07:13.795 --> 00:07:21.918
'How did you know this? Do you have somebody on the inside?'I said, 'No, it's all Jesus.'And I have to explain to law enforcement quite often.

00:07:21.919 --> 00:07:31.479
I want you to know I do this all for Him. I told you as soon as He tells me to turn this channel off, I'll ride away in the sunset.

00:07:31.480 --> 00:07:40.151
There's nothing you can give me, honest to God, that my wife hasn't worked eight years for a degree and is very good at it.

00:07:40.152 --> 00:07:44.992
The same with me; I could do other things to help out around the house.

00:07:44.993 --> 00:07:50.723
I raised dogs. I raised all these things. We did this because the Lord asked us to do it.

00:07:50.724 --> 00:07:55.933
Yes. And it hasn't been easy. It hasn't been easy. And there's people that say I'm a false prophet.

00:07:55.934 --> 00:08:01.992
You say I'm fake. I'm all these things. That's on you. I don't care what you really think.

00:08:01.993 --> 00:08:08.062
Whenever the rubber meets the road and you see, and I'm standing before my King, I'll be held accountable by Him.

00:08:08.063 --> 00:08:18.399
If I've led anybody astray by any words I give, I take it very seriously. This is a very heavy responsibility.

00:08:18.400 --> 00:08:26.319
Nobody will understand the pressure that I'm under on a 99% basis and crying myself to sleep because of the pressure.

00:08:26.320 --> 00:08:33.232
I want you to understand. We come back on here with a smile on our face. I'm always transparent.

00:08:33.233 --> 00:08:39.519
I don't tell you where I live on purpose because there are crazy people trying to hurt me.

00:08:39.520 --> 00:08:42.995
Do you understand? Now, people want to try to expose me and say, 'Hey, this is where he's at.

00:08:42.996 --> 00:08:45.562
This is where he's at.'I have to buy another house. I have to do this.

00:08:45.563 --> 00:08:49.510
I have to get away. Hey, listen. I have... the Lord has blessed my wife.

00:08:49.511 --> 00:08:56.080
We're blessed. So, like I said, I'm not trying to take anything from you all.

00:08:56.081 --> 00:09:05.894
If you want to bless my family, that's on you. That's on you. But like I said, the Lord said go on YouTube and ask them for nothing.

00:09:05.895 --> 00:09:11.731
Nothing. And over the... it's like one of the things I want to say this.

00:09:11.732 --> 00:09:21.159
When XRP was at 12 cents—and I'll say this, this is the only thing—I was buying.

00:09:21.160 --> 00:09:28.270
He tells me when to buy and he tells me when to sell. He tells me when silver's going up.

00:09:28.271 --> 00:09:36.721
He tells me when it crashes. I hear him very well, but I don't brag and I don't try to flex.

00:09:36.722 --> 00:09:39.719
People see it around the church and people get mad and they get jealous.

00:09:39.720 --> 00:09:46.795
Everything that I'm telling you is the truth, but I'm transparent about it.

00:09:46.796 --> 00:09:51.143
We're very transparent. I have nothing to hide from you. I have nothing to gain from you.

00:09:51.144 --> 00:09:56.474
I do these videos and I do all this for the glory of God. So, I wanted to make that very clear tonight.

00:09:56.475 --> 00:10:01.799
There's people that are very angry and I've gotten the emails and I say, 'Hey, man.

00:10:01.800 --> 00:10:07.753
We never asked you for a dime. I've never tried to solicit you. I don't sell books.

00:10:07.754 --> 00:10:21.759
I don't try to sell books.'I have been offered to put ads—like to make an ad on live—$100,000 a month to do ads and do things for this one company.

00:10:21.760 --> 00:10:31.149
And I told them no. The Lord said no. All I had to do was just do a little segment and put it on all my channels throughout all the world.

00:10:31.150 --> 00:10:44.399
I have seven channels—eight now. Put them on all those channels at the beginning for just a two-minute segment and they give me $100,000 a month.

00:10:44.400 --> 00:10:51.205
My flesh wanted to take that money. I'm not going to lie to you. I was like, 'That's over a million dollars a year.

00:10:51.206 --> 00:11:00.759
Of course, we'll do it.'And Diana goes, 'You took a vow to God. You will not take that money.

00:11:00.760 --> 00:11:14.833
We will not take that money.'Then I had a businessman fly in from Japan who told me he would let me fly around in his private jet for free and give me hundreds of thousands of dollars to be his friend and give him financial advice and things.

00:11:14.834 --> 00:11:29.241
I do not give financial advice to anyone. We fear God more than people realize. They don't know us. It is everything. This life goes away.

00:11:29.242 --> 00:11:37.528
But when we get to heaven, a lot of people put so much into what they feel like they can do on earth.

00:11:37.529 --> 00:11:43.319
But it's really about what we can do. What we are doing now is affecting our eternity for the kingdom.

00:11:43.320 --> 00:11:50.372
And I take it very seriously, very, very seriously, to work for the Lord, to do what we're doing.

00:11:50.373 --> 00:11:55.599
And I'm behind the scenes just doing what I've done for years, just doing my eBay and Poshmark.

00:11:55.600 --> 00:12:04.679
Done this for a long time—at least a decade. Over a decade. So, and taxes, things that you can do.

00:12:04.680 --> 00:12:09.759
You do understand when you have a master's degree, why you don't let it die.

00:12:09.760 --> 00:12:15.066
She worked. She went to school for forever—over eight years.

00:12:15.067 --> 00:12:19.742
And I told her, I said, 'I'm not asking you to give up your education to do this.

00:12:19.743 --> 00:12:23.730
If God calls you to come beside me, that's fine, baby. I understand.

00:12:23.731 --> 00:12:31.319
We don't want what we've done for years that has provided for us to die.'So, I want to make that clear.

00:12:31.320 --> 00:12:38.913
She homeschools and does the things that we do. It's a lot. But Diana is a full-time working person plus homeschools.

00:12:38.914 --> 00:12:55.039
And then she sends out thank you letters to the people that have blessed us and says, 'Listen, she writes every single one of them out by hand.'She writes it and she does things and she goes, 'Brandon, I feel like they deserve a thank you.'I said, 'Diana, you don't have time for this.

00:12:55.040 --> 00:13:10.275
People—I just think y'all are so kind. There's so many people that just love us and just love what we're doing for God.'And it's all many hands on deck as we're doing this final push, as he's coming so soon.

00:13:10.276 --> 00:13:22.329
And there's such an urgency of the hour. I know people say, 'Well, they've been saying he's going to come back for so long,'but he is coming so soon.

00:13:22.330 --> 00:13:32.439
And I take it very seriously that I'll take any load I can off of him so that he can keep going, so we can keep going for the Lord.

00:13:32.440 --> 00:13:37.792
We do it all for the Lord. I'd give everything away. It doesn't matter. Nothing matters to me.

00:13:37.793 --> 00:13:48.759
It's just keeping on course and finishing this race and doing it with everything we have so that we can stand before our king and go, 'We did our best we could.

00:13:48.760 --> 00:13:54.479
I tried my best,'you know? And I can see, you know, we believe every day Megan's going to get healed.

00:13:54.480 --> 00:13:58.927
But one day, I know for sure there's going to be a day—if it's not here, it's there.

00:13:58.928 --> 00:14:11.393
So now I have to hire full-time security that's going to cost me over $100,000 a year because I have idiots that want to know where I live. And I said, 'Well, I knew it was coming.

00:14:11.394 --> 00:14:27.908
The Lord told me: I'm going to make you a household name.'He said, 'You're going to be known all around the world and it's happening.'And he said, 'And in doing so, like Oral Roberts had to have security 24/7 and other ministries, you will have to also.'So I've already looked into it today.

00:14:27.909 --> 00:14:35.117
I'm telling you, it's going to cost me a ton of money, but it is what it is, and it's part of the price of doing what God's called me to do.

00:14:35.118 --> 00:14:41.639
So, I'll have an armed guard continually at my home. That sucks, but it is what it is.

00:14:41.640 --> 00:14:49.479
And he'll travel with me to services so maybe I'll start going to other people's ministries because I'll have security now.

00:14:49.480 --> 00:15:01.239
You know, I thought I could start taking preaching engagements and not have to worry if the church has security anymore because I'll have somebody—ex-military is what I'm looking into.

00:15:01.240 --> 00:15:09.279
And having this ex-military 24/7, seven days a week around me and my wife and my kids because of the threats I get.

00:15:09.280 --> 00:15:20.439
So, I appreciate your prayers. I truly do. It has been very hard.

00:15:20.440 --> 00:15:35.753
I never knew some of the things that I would say would bring up so much hatred by so many different groups of people that are not playing around when it comes to your life.

00:15:35.754 --> 00:15:50.959
I didn't realize, you know, when you see politicians get their lives threatened and you see John Hagee in the past—the guy missed him six times, shooting at him and all the things. This stuff's real. Charlie Kirk's real.

00:15:50.960 --> 00:16:11.541
And there comes a point in time where the world doesn't understand the value of life and just having a man just doing what he's called to do, praying online with thousands and hundreds of thousands every time I do this—hundreds of thousands of people worldwide.

00:16:11.542 --> 00:16:19.519
This is so much more than I ever dreamed: the pressure and the responsibility of it.

00:16:19.520 --> 00:16:30.079
Making sure you're not flaky and making sure you're accurate so that you represent him well.

00:16:30.080 --> 00:16:35.599
And the week that we've had and the last two weeks we've had, it has been really rough.

00:16:35.600 --> 00:16:42.829
But I give all glory and honor because he said you'll be persecuted for the word's sake. And then he warned me.

00:16:42.830 --> 00:16:49.029
He said, 'The one person who's persecuting you, Brandon, will be dead within 16 months.'And he warned me about it.

00:16:49.030 --> 00:16:58.019
And I said, 'Lord, spare their life. Protect them. Protect them.'He said they've opened a door and because of this door, they're going to be gone in 16 months.

00:16:58.020 --> 00:17:02.979
And I don't know what that means, but I've been interceding for them all day long.

00:17:02.980 --> 00:17:06.079
Praying for these people, praying for the people who persecute.

00:17:06.080 --> 00:17:11.039
Like I said, we love you. We forgive people. We're not holding a grudge towards anyone.

00:17:11.040 --> 00:17:13.309
We have a child with special needs. We do all these things and Diana, like I said, works her tail end off.

00:17:13.310 --> 00:17:13.409
I'm thankful for all the people who like, subscribe, click the notification bell, and I'm thankful for YouTube.

00:17:13.410 --> 00:17:13.509
They pay me well for all the ads and it's been, like I said, I do that and I go, 'Hey, man, Lord, you've taken care of things.'It is what it is.

00:17:13.510 --> 00:17:13.709
I have seven channels. Each one gets tens of thousands of views.

00:17:13.710 --> 00:17:17.438
It's all because he's blessed it. And when we got monetized on X, I was shocked.

00:17:17.439 --> 00:17:23.113
And when it's time for us to go off YouTube, if he ever tells us to, when I was monetized on Facebook and X, I was shocked.

00:17:23.114 --> 00:17:33.239
I really was because it takes a lot to get monetized on X. It's hard. But he pays me every month now—Elon.

00:17:33.240 --> 00:17:43.190
And I go, 'Hey, it's all glory to God.'"I'm just being transparent with you."It is what it is.

00:17:43.191 --> 00:17:50.798
I just wanted to be very upfront with everybody because I truly have nothing to hide.

00:17:50.799 --> 00:18:00.159
I hide things from you, like a house or whatever, for the protection of my kids because of the threats I've had on my life.

00:18:00.160 --> 00:18:04.159
Other than that, if I didn't have kids, I'd put it all up. I don't care.

00:18:04.160 --> 00:18:10.452
You can come to my house and have tea; I have nothing to hide. We work our rears off. Come over and have a glass of tea.

00:18:10.453 --> 00:18:23.346
But when you have crazies coming up in here saying, "Hey, we have guns and we want to hurt you,"you go, "Well, that's probably not a good idea."So now I have to have security.

00:18:23.347 --> 00:18:28.334
God bless it, I don't want people around my wife and me all the time.

00:18:28.335 --> 00:18:32.679
I'm very private, and having a bodyguard is going to be very awkward.

00:18:32.680 --> 00:18:38.999
But as of this week, things have changed, so we have to have a bodyguard.

00:18:39.000 --> 00:18:46.044
We appreciate y'all. We really do. We love you. So, let's pray. Now, how was that?

00:18:46.045 --> 00:18:52.879
I tried to clear it up and be as transparent as I could tonight because of the emails we've gotten today over the last couple of days.

00:18:52.880 --> 00:19:01.558
That's where you go for that. Let's see some of the things we've had in the news.

00:19:01.559 --> 00:19:16.879
I wanted you to show me about another thing people say: "Why do you have this?"This is for entertainment purposes only because I was instructed to by my attorney.

00:19:16.880 --> 00:19:24.083
Anything I say is for entertainment purposes only. He said you have to put that underneath there.

00:19:24.084 --> 00:19:28.435
Bo Polny and all these other people have it on there, and he showed me.

00:19:28.436 --> 00:19:39.840
I have three attorneys. They all say the same thing, so I do exactly what I've been told to do. Is that what people want to say?

00:19:39.841 --> 00:19:48.275
"Well, are you doing it for entertainment or is this prophetic?"Brother, it is what I was instructed to do by law.

00:19:48.276 --> 00:19:53.427
There are crazy people out there. So just letting you know. I mean, I try, like I said—why do you have certain things?

00:19:53.428 --> 00:19:56.399
Why do you do this? Why do you do that? This is it. This is real.

00:19:56.400 --> 00:20:05.239
But I wanted to show you her awards and that Diana is a hardworking person; she has her master's.

00:20:05.240 --> 00:20:14.399
And so, like I said, I'm never going to apologize for what we have—our cars, anything—never, because we work our rears off for it.

00:20:14.400 --> 00:20:18.719
Look at this right here; I want to show you these earthquakes. Do you see this?

