According to an alert viewed by ABC, this is exactly what I tried to tell you all. They were going to use drones; I've said it over and over.

00:20:43.571 --> 00:20:58.959
Every single time I see the drones coming into the stadiums in baseball, they had explosive devices on these drones and they ignited them.

