00:21:47.052 --> 00:22:00.159
And the Lord said specifically, even in the last video, "Remember, this is what the Lord showed us clear back then."Go back and watch.

00:22:00.160 --> 00:22:07.816
Can we watch that video again? "A very strong magnitude 6.0 earthquake struck near Naples, Italy, shortly after midnight on March 10th, 2026.

00:22:07.817 --> 00:22:12.651
This is the strongest earthquake to hit this part of Italy in more than 63 years.

00:22:12.652 --> 00:22:29.799
The last quake of equal or greater strength near the same area was a magnitude 7.0 earthquake on March 28th, 1963."That's what the Lord warned us was going to start to manifest all over Italy.

00:22:29.800 --> 00:22:43.048
And the Lord said, "Before the big one in the water"—and if we look at what we saw coming out of the water, I saw over 300,000 people will perish on the coastline.

