It only lasts for a window."And then you'll hear President Trump come out with a plan in the future where he'll say, "Drill, baby, drill."They'll say there's oil in the Mediterranean outside of Gaza, and Israel will start to drill oil in Gaza and the area, and they will bring forth a lot of money.

