02:30:24.969 --> 02:30:42.749
I heard my friend Billy Burke say one time, "The reason why people fall, Brandon, is they're empty."The reason why people stay in sin and they're looking at bad things on the internet, they're drinking, they're doing all these bad things that they shouldn't be doing, strung out, is because they're empty.

