02:31:22.078 --> 02:31:26.466
I'm dealing with all this stuff."That means your level of the Word is empty.

02:31:26.467 --> 02:31:30.311
You're going too low. You've got to get full of the Word of God.

02:31:30.312 --> 02:31:35.166
And the more the Word of God is inside of you, the more it will change you from the inside out.

02:31:35.167 --> 02:31:41.879
But if you're low on Word, the devil comes as a thief and he's going to kill, steal, and destroy everything you've got.

02:31:41.880 --> 02:31:59.616
Remember that it's the Word that he's afraid of, not prayer. The Bible didn't say that prayer is a sword. It's the Word.

02:31:59.617 --> 02:32:09.035
The only way you're ever going to get rid of the devil in your life and temptations and addictions—you'll know the truth, and the truth will set you free.

02:32:09.036 --> 02:32:13.959
What's the truth? The Word of God. So, you've got to say that Word out of your mouth.

02:32:13.960 --> 02:32:22.559
