02:33:39.880 --> 02:33:45.119
And it comes out of you like a tidal wave of glory. Boom! The devil goes, 'Ah!'and he runs.

02:33:45.120 --> 02:33:56.079
But if you don't have that, you go, 'I'm just praying, "This little light of mine, I'm going to let it shine."Devil, leave me alone.'He isn't going to listen to you; he isn't afraid of that.

02:33:56.080 --> 02:34:10.639
