02:34:10.640 --> 02:34:19.634
What are they saying out of their mouth? The Word of God will change you from the inside out.

02:34:19.635 --> 02:34:24.963
And if you aren't saying that Word out of your mouth, I don't care how much prayer you're doing.

02:34:24.964 --> 02:34:35.799
