02:36:22.840 --> 02:36:35.639
He spoke the Word. And the moment he spoke the Word, the devil was like, 'Oh, he knows the truth. He's Jesus.

02:36:35.640 --> 02:36:50.119
There's something about that; I better leave him.''If you be the Son of God, turn this stone into bread.''Man shall not live by bread alone, but every word that proceedeth out of the mouth of God.'Slap him in the face!

02:36:50.120 --> 02:36:55.959
But he never prayed him away; he used the Word out of his mouth to get rid of him.

02:36:55.960 --> 02:37:06.199
His full fought for him. Jesus was full. And the moment he spoke it out of his mouth, that's when the devil fled.

02:37:06.200 --> 02:37:17.239
He came to tempt our Savior, and His full fought for him. You understand? So you have to let your full fight for you.

02:37:17.240 --> 02:37:21.712
You cannot be empty in these last days and think you're going to submit yourself and resist.

02:37:21.713 --> 02:37:26.879
You think you've got all these temptations, all these addictions—it's because you're empty.

02:37:26.880 --> 02:37:35.412
Fill yourself up with the Word of God continually, and the truth you know will set you free. Calling those things that be not as though they were.

02:37:35.413 --> 02:37:47.577
I'm free from this addiction of nicotine, alcoholism, pornography, and whatever else you deal with—drugs, opioids, it doesn't matter.

02:37:47.578 --> 02:37:52.302
All of it's underneath the blood. All of it's underneath the authority of the believer.

02:37:52.303 --> 02:38:07.879
And if you don't have that Word in your heart, I don't want to hear you complaining, saying, 'Well, Brandon, I've prayed.'It's not about prayer alone; you must have the Word inside of you to remain free in these last days.

02:38:07.880 --> 02:38:15.759
That concerns your finances, your health, and your mental well-being.

02:38:15.760 --> 02:38:27.359
Second Timothy 1:7 says that God has not given me a spirit of fear, but of power and of love and of a well-balanced mind.

